column5: There's good news.Wayne Clark at KCs Landing on Edward Lake went out and drilled a hole where ice shacks will sit pretty soon and had 6" of solid ice and caught 4 walleyes in a hurry.Bad news is he didn't invite me.lol.So might have to go and get a fresh feed of fish soon.
Whoa,,,whoa,,,, let's put the brakes on for awhile!!
Just want to make sure ice is good and right spot.Iam going Wednesday nice looking sunny day.
Just make sure you leave enough for the rest of us.I'm looking at a divorce if I don't put my wife on a load of eyes,i promised her.lol
Lol.your safe first ice always best.
I wanna give those killer krumbs a work out.
I can get some from coop if you want
I can stop on the way n get some,but thanks for the offer.
Following in your footsteps. Literally. I wish. Expectations of accounting for each trip! Bill
